<SEQUENCE>2
<FILENAME>noticeofchangeofauditor.htm
<DESCRIPTION>NOTICE OF CHANGE OF AUDITOR
<TEXT>
<!doctype html public "-//IETF//DTD HTML//EN">
<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Notice of Change of Auditor</TITLE>
<META NAME="date" CONTENT="07/03/2015">
</HEAD>
<BODY style="margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:10pt; 
color:#000000">
<P style="margin:0px"><BR></P>
<P style="margin:0px"><BR></P>
<P style="margin:0px"><img src="noticeofchangeofauditor001.jpg" 
alt="[noticeofchangeofauditor001.jpg]" align=middle height=50.733 
width=229.133></P>
<P style="margin:0px"><BR></P>
<P style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:-2px; width:48px; font-family:Arial; 
font-size:11pt; float:left"><B>To:</B></P>
<P style="margin:0px; padding-left:48px; text-indent:-2px; font-family:Arial; 
font-size:11pt"><B>Alberta Securities Commission</B></P>
<P style="margin:0px; padding-left:48px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; 
clear:left"><B>British Columbia Securities Commission</B></P>
<P style="margin:0px; padding-left:48px; font-family:Arial; font-
size:11pt"><B>Deloitte s.e.n.c.r.l. (&#171;&nbsp;Deloitte&nbsp;&#187;)</B></P>
<P style="margin:0px; padding-left:48px; font-family:Arial; font-
size:11pt"><B>KPMG s.e.n.c.r.l. (&#171;&nbsp;KPMG&nbsp;&#187;)</B></P>
<P style="margin:0px"><BR></P>
<P style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:-2px; width:48px; font-family:Arial; 
font-size:11pt; float:left"><B>Re&nbsp;:</B></P>
<P style="margin:0px; text-indent:-2px; font-family:Arial; font-
size:11pt"><B>NOTICE OF CHANGE OF AUDITORS FOR CLIFTON STAR RESOURCES INC. 
(&#147;the Corporation&#148;)</B></P>
<P style="margin:0px; clear:left"><BR></P>
<P style="margin:0px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt" align=justify>Pursuant 
to National Instrument 51-102, Clifton Star Resources Inc. hereby provides 
change of auditor notice as follows:</P>
<P style="margin:0px" align=justify><BR></P>
<P style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:-2px; text-indent:24px; width:48px; 
font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; float:left">1.</P>
<P style="margin:0px; padding-left:48px; text-indent:-2px; font-family:Arial; 
font-size:11pt" align=justify>Deloitte of Montreal, Quebec, resigned as the 
Corporation&#146;s auditor, at the Corporation request, on June 17, 2015.</P>
<P style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:-2px; text-indent:24px; width:48px; 
font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; clear:left; float:left">2.</P>
<P style="margin:0px; padding-left:48px; text-indent:-2px; font-family:Arial; 
font-size:11pt" align=justify>On June 17, 2015, the Corporation appointed KPMG 
of Montreal, Quebec, to fill the vacancy created by the resignation of Deloitte,
and to hold such position until the close of the next annual meeting of 
shareholders of the Company.</P>
<P style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:-2px; text-indent:24px; width:48px; 
font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; clear:left; float:left">3.</P>
<P style="margin:0px; padding-left:48px; text-indent:-2px; font-family:Arial; 
font-size:11pt" align=justify>The resignation of Deloitte and the appointment of
KPMG was considered and approved by the Board of Directors of the 
Corporation.</P>
<P style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:-2px; text-indent:24px; width:48px; 
font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; clear:left; float:left">4.</P>
<P style="margin:0px; padding-left:48px; text-indent:-2px; font-family:Arial; 
font-size:11pt" align=justify>There were no modifications of opinion by Deloitte
in the Auditor&#146;s Reports of the two most recently completed fiscal years 
ended June 30, 2014 and June 30, 2013.</P>
<P style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:-2px; text-indent:24px; width:48px; 
font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; clear:left; float:left">5.</P>
<P style="margin:0px; padding-left:48px; text-indent:-2px; font-family:Arial; 
font-size:11pt" align=justify>The Board of Directors of the Corporation is of 
the opinion that there were no &#147;reportable events&#148; as defined by 
National Instrument 51-102, which occurred in connection with the audit of the 
two most recently completed fiscal years or for any period subsequent to the 
most recently completed fiscal period for which an Auditor&#146;s Report was 
issued.</P>
<P style="margin:0px; clear:left" align=justify><BR></P>
<P style="margin:0px" align=justify><BR></P>
<P style="margin:0px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt" align=justify>Dated at 
the City of Quebec, in the province of Quebec, this 17th day of June, 2015.</P>
<P style="margin:0px" align=justify><BR></P>
<P style="margin:0px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt" align=justify>Yours 
very truly,</P>
<P style="margin:0px" align=justify><BR></P>
<P style="margin:0px" align=justify><BR></P>
<P style="margin:0px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt" align=justify>(s) 
Michel Bouchard</P>
<P style="margin:0px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt" 
align=justify>________________________________</P>
<P style="margin:0px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt" align=justify><B>Michel
Bouchard</B></P>
<P style="margin:0px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt" 
align=justify><B>President and Chief Executive Officer</B></P>
<P style="margin:0px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt" 
align=justify><B>CLIFTON STAR RESOURCES INC.</B></P>
<P style="margin:0px"><BR></P>
<P style="margin:0px"><BR>
<BR></P>
</BODY>

<P style="margin:0px; font-size:11pt"><B>Re: Notice of Change of Auditors for

<P style="margin:0px"><BR></P>
<P style="margin:0px; font-size:11pt">We have read the Notice of Change of 
Auditors for Clifton Star Resources Inc. dated June&nbsp;17, 2015 and are in 
agreement with the statements contained in such Notice, except that we are not 
in a position to agree or disagree with the Company&#146;s statement in items 4 
and 5.</P>
<P style="margin:0px" align=justify><BR></P>
<P style="margin:0px; font-size:11pt" align=justify>Yours very truly,</P>
